text: LA-34 is a constituency of Azad Kashmir Legislative Assembly which is currently represented by Chaudhary Javid Akhtar of Pakistan Muslim League (N). It covers the area of Gujrat District Wazirabad Tehsil Mandi Bahauddin District in Pakistan. Only refugees from Jammu and Ladakh settled in Pakistan are eligible to vote. ==Election 2016== elections were held in this constituency on 21 July 2016.
